# Scam Hunters Journey Map (with Artifact References)

This document maps the user experience across all primary entry points into the Scamâ€¯Hunters ecosystem. Each node is linked to specific artifacts (see `artifact_index.md`â€¯now structured with optional YAML metadata for automation) and includes user intent, content block, and expected behavior.

